title: Photos: Pro Buhari solidarity rally in Port Harcourt
text:
Home » News » Photos: Pro Buhari solidarity rally in Port Harcourt Photos: Pro Buhari solidarity rally in Port Harcourt On 3:14 pm In News by adekunle Comments 
Youths from across various Local Government Area in Rivers State Tuesday staged a pro Buhari solidarity rally in Port Harcourt . 
The rally was organised by a conglomeration of Civil Society organisations in the State L-R Robertson Jack, Chairman, Movement for Positive Change; Engr Irieye Jack, Head, Technical Committee, Conglomeration of Civil Society Coalition and Mr Abiye Tomquin, Public Relation Officer, Rivers Success Movement during a Pro Buhari Solidarity Briefing in Port Harcourt organised by A Conglomeration of Civil Society organisations in the State Tuesday.
